114
00:07:51,300 --> 00:07:52,460
Don't tell Wanyue

115
00:07:54,460 --> 00:07:55,340
that I'm dying.

116
00:07:56,980 --> 00:07:58,940
I just want to see her happy
for a little longer.

117
00:07:59,700 --> 00:08:00,700
I want to see her

118
00:08:01,820 --> 00:08:02,980
smile for a little longer.

119
00:08:04,620 --> 00:08:05,300
Will you?

120
00:08:06,740 --> 00:08:07,820
Ms. Xu, tell me.

121
00:08:08,540 --> 00:08:09,940
How much longer does he have?

122
00:08:10,700 --> 00:08:11,900
These past days,

123
00:08:12,140 --> 00:08:14,300
he's been relying entirely on medicine.

124
00:08:14,940 --> 00:08:15,860
Tomorrow,

125
00:08:16,380 --> 00:08:19,340
his vision will be completely gone.

126
00:08:20,300 --> 00:08:22,460
When he goes completely blind,

127
00:08:23,140 --> 00:08:25,380
