128
00:08:29,900 --> 00:08:30,580
Young Master,

129
00:08:31,220 --> 00:08:32,300
I've decided.

130
00:08:32,900 --> 00:08:34,140
Our little puppy,

131
00:08:34,860 --> 00:08:35,700
let's call it

132
00:08:35,900 --> 00:08:36,820
Pear Candy,

133
00:08:37,180 --> 00:08:38,060
