136
00:08:43,620 --> 00:08:44,660
every day.

137
00:08:46,580 --> 00:08:47,980
You promised me.

138
00:09:22,020 --> 00:09:23,660
Come, let's eat.

139
00:09:23,900 --> 00:09:24,740
