144
00:10:12,580 --> 00:10:13,100
Sure.

145
00:10:13,880 --> 00:10:15,060
Let's bring Pear Candy along.

146
00:10:15,900 --> 00:10:16,540
Alright.

147
00:10:34,620 --> 00:10:35,060
Come on,

148
00:10:35,180 --> 00:10:35,780
Pear Candy.

149
00:10:36,940 --> 00:10:37,660
Wanyue,

150
00:10:38,180 --> 00:10:39,300
