151
00:10:39,740 --> 00:10:40,860
Then let's sit here.

152
00:10:41,220 --> 00:10:41,700
Alright.

153
00:10:41,860 --> 00:10:42,300
Here.

154
00:10:53,300 --> 00:10:54,100
Wanyue.

155
00:10:55,180 --> 00:10:56,060
I want

156
00:10:56,140 --> 00:10:57,860
to eat another pear candy.

157
00:10:58,740 --> 00:10:59,340
Alright.

158
00:11:02,860 --> 00:11:03,340
Here.

159
00:11:18,660 --> 00:11:19,740
The first time in my life

160
00:11:20,100 --> 00:11:22,020
I ever ate pear candy

161
00:11:22,700 --> 00:11:24,340
was from you.

162
00:11:29,100 --> 00:11:32,140
One candy, and the pain will go away.

163
00:11:39,660 --> 00:11:40,620
Back then,

164
00:11:42,140 --> 00:11:43,780
I still called you "Miss."

165
00:11:46,340 --> 00:11:47,260
Now,

166
00:11:47,700 --> 00:11:49,140
I call you "Young Master."

167
00:11:51,700 --> 00:11:52,580
Miss.

168
00:11:55,940 --> 00:11:56,740
Young Master.

169
00:12:02,740 --> 00:12:03,540
Miss.

170
00:12:05,740 --> 00:12:07,300
I feel a little sleepy.

171
00:12:08,620 --> 00:12:09,780
I want to rest for a while.

172
00:12:12,700 --> 00:12:13,300
Sleep.

173
00:12:15,860 --> 00:12:17,100
Remember to wake me up.

174
00:12:18,620 --> 00:12:19,820
Later, our Young Master still

175
00:12:20,300 --> 00:12:21,860
has to go home and practice calligraphy.

176
00:12:22,380 --> 00:12:23,100
Alright.

