208
00:15:17,260 --> 00:15:18,660
(I've likely already passed.)

209
00:15:19,340 --> 00:15:20,420
(To Wanyue)

210
00:15:20,420 --> 00:15:22,460
(If I had never met you in this life,)

211
00:15:23,660 --> 00:15:26,500
(perhaps I'd have long ceased
to linger in this world.)

212
00:15:28,100 --> 00:15:29,860
(Perhaps I'd have left
this world long ago.)

213
00:15:32,780 --> 00:15:34,620
(I often thought fate was unfair to me.)

214
00:15:35,660 --> 00:15:37,500
(But whenever I stood by your side)

215
00:15:37,980 --> 00:15:39,180
(holding your hand,)

216
00:15:40,140 --> 00:15:41,020
(I felt grateful)

217
00:15:41,820 --> 00:15:43,420
(for the kindness fate has shown me.)

218
00:15:45,460 --> 00:15:47,180
(I don't know why I love you,)

219
00:15:48,500 --> 00:15:51,660
(just as I don't know
why people live and die.)

220
00:15:53,110 --> 00:15:54,540
(But I know deeply that I love you.)

221
00:15:55,740 --> 00:15:56,780
Don't let her know.

222
00:15:58,860 --> 00:15:59,340
Never come

223
00:15:59,860 --> 00:16:00,860
looking for me again.

224
00:16:01,140 --> 00:16:02,340
(I originally planned)

225
00:16:02,740 --> 00:16:05,020
(to leave silently before death arrived)

226
00:16:05,700 --> 00:16:06,860
(to face it alone,)

227
00:16:07,460 --> 00:16:09,260
(but in the end, I lacked the courage.)

228
00:16:09,660 --> 00:16:10,740
Don't tell Wanyue

229
00:16:12,140 --> 00:16:13,140
that I'm dying.

230
00:16:13,380 --> 00:16:14,860
(So please forgive me)

231
00:16:15,300 --> 00:16:17,580
(for not telling you
about my illness sooner.)

232
00:16:18,380 --> 00:16:20,100
(Selfishly, I feared
breaking your heart.)

233
00:16:20,780 --> 00:16:21,700
(Selfishly,)

234
00:16:22,320 --> 00:16:24,260
(I only wished to spend
the last days of my life)

235
00:16:24,260 --> 00:16:25,460
(watching your smile.)

236
00:16:26,580 --> 00:16:27,580
(Selfishly,)

237
00:16:28,340 --> 00:16:29,780
(I left before you.)

238
00:16:31,100 --> 00:16:32,020
(Please forgive me.)

239
00:16:32,540 --> 00:16:34,420
(From now on,
I'll no longer be by your side.)

240
00:16:36,020 --> 00:16:36,740
(Wanyue,)

241
00:16:38,260 --> 00:16:40,740
(I don't know if the days ahead
will be better.)

242
00:16:42,060 --> 00:16:44,940
(I worry that one day,
war will reach our village.)

243
00:16:46,620 --> 00:16:47,780
(That you'll long for a hug,)

244
00:16:47,780 --> 00:16:49,180
(but no one will give you one.)

245
00:16:51,180 --> 00:16:53,060
(But I don't have much time left.)

246
00:16:55,100 --> 00:16:57,020
(So I brought many pear seeds)

247
00:16:57,900 --> 00:16:59,580
(to let them be buried with me.)

248
00:17:00,700 --> 00:17:02,060
(My shade)

249
00:17:02,700 --> 00:17:04,340
(will always be here waiting for you.)

250
00:17:05,660 --> 00:17:06,460
(Wanyue,)

251
00:17:07,860 --> 00:17:09,300
(you must live on.)

252
00:17:10,940 --> 00:17:12,300
(You promised me)

253
00:17:13,340 --> 00:17:14,580
(to be my eyes)

254
00:17:16,180 --> 00:17:17,580
(and to see the world for me.)

255
00:17:19,340 --> 00:17:21,220
(You must see enough,)

256
00:17:21,220 --> 00:17:22,220
(then come find me,)

257
00:17:23,580 --> 00:17:25,100
(and tell me)

258
00:17:27,300 --> 00:17:28,700
(the stories of this world.)

259
