♪Memories entwine reality♪

262
00:17:45,260 --> 00:17:49,380
♪The cycle of stars continues,
only you anchor me♪

263
00:17:49,380 --> 00:17:52,220
♪Through joys and sorrows♪

264
00:17:52,540 --> 00:17:55,820
♪So many obsessions, all in vain♪

265
00:17:55,980 --> 00:17:59,500
♪So many promises,
ultimately unfulfilled♪

266
00:17:59,780 --> 00:18:05,780
♪I only hope to be with you♪

